  "description": "Everything you have ever seen, touched, or tasted is made of protons, neutrons, and electrons. This ordinary matter -- [baryonic matter](../terms/baryonic-matter.md) -- accounts for every star, every planet, every grain of dust, every living thing. It is also less than five percent of the universe.",
